2019-06-26T03:02:00.000Z","msg":"佢公司有新男同事，近排佢哋一班人成日食晏，可能佢睇中咗個男同事，又唔想做衰人，所以想我講分手，自己就好走啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢成日提起個男同事，但個男仔對我女朋友好似無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢好驚俾人話，所以唔想做講分手嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa0898a9105fb1d054bfde05e796282adf85916","tid":1257873,"uid":263312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"兩個人一齊都係想開心想感受到被愛啫，如果一齊仲唔開心過自己一個，咁不如分手喇"},{"pid":"1bb4c7a99cd0de7c83b77536e3c42c18766ca6f8","tid":1257873,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a06f671bfbb2bf842481d63e0a22cb46a11997","tid":1257873,"uid":161428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bb5fcd9b200873c1fa7377e209392afba3440ba","tid":1257873,"uid":268770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:41:23.000Z","msg":"一齊左就快兩年<br />\n兩年間成日都feel到佢我地真係好唔岩<br />\n有好多野 講完佢都唔明 所以我唔講<br />\n磨合左知大家點相處<br />\n我邊個位應該忍 忍左個啲位就唔會鬧交<br />\n但係相處得唔開心<br />\n好多野佢都好似奉旨咁<br />\n同埋可以全日都唔搵我<br />\n我信佢冇第二個<br />\n但係我會諗其實你有冇諗起過我<br />\n<br />\n其實係冇一樣野爆出黎令到嘈到分手<br />\n依家關係好平靜<br />\n都唔知點講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"你需要釐清你同你男朋友嘅價值觀係咪一樣或者差唔多，唔同愛情觀嘅情侶好難一生一世，就算性格幾夾都好⋯"},{"pid":"a7c0e994ebf2f16f23df755065aa41de1f0efa84","tid":1257873,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d450e849e3680fc32d39e7c8bf358c433f64146","tid":1257873,"uid":257176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r